The correct structure should be:

```json
"SessionStart": [
  {
    "type": "command",
    "command": "..."
  }
]
```

NOT:

```json
"SessionStart": [
  {
    "hooks": [
      {
        "type": "command",
        "command": "..."
      }
    ]
  }
]
```

